<heading> UCI Podcast talks about Brilliant Future with campaign director Karen Isble </heading>
<sub_heading> N/A </sub_heading>
<date> October 4, 2019 </date>
<article> UCI officially launched its Brilliant Future philanthropic campaign on Oct. 4, 2019, with a goal of raising $2 billion to fund scientific research, provide scholarships for students, advance healthcare innovations, and foster deeper explorations into our shared human experience. In this episode of the UCI Podcast, host Tom Vasich delves into the campaign with one of its behind-the-scenes leaders, Karen Isble, associate vice chancellor & campaign director of University Advancement.

 
 
 
 
  </article>
